{"item_id":"6491263f8b:0","text":"Materials 控制对象的外观，而 patterns 通过在 surface 上改变 material 的 Bxdf 参数来控制细节。"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:1","text":"这类似 texture artists 使用 textures 来控制 material 外观的方式。"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:2","text":"RenderMan 附带了一组 patterns，可用于 texturing、color correction、bumping 以及各种 utility shading systems。"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:3","text":"这些 patterns 可以分为以下类别："}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:4","text":"程序化纹理（Procedural Textures）类别"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:5","text":"以程序化方式创建 noise 和 patterns。"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:6","text":"PxrChecker"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:7","text":"PxrCurvature"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:8","text":"PxrFractal"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:9","text":"PxrVoronoise"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:10","text":"PxrWorley"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:11","text":"PxrPhasorNoise"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:12","text":"颜色节点（Color Nodes）类型"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:13","text":"在 shading network 中创建或修改颜色。"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:14","text":"PxrBlackBody"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:15","text":"PxrBlend"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:16","text":"PxrClamp"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:17","text":"PxrColorCorrect"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:18","text":"PxrColorSpace"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:19","text":"PxrExposure"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:20","text":"PxrGamma"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:21","text":"PxrHairColor"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:22","text":"PxrHSL"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:23","text":"PxrInvert"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:24","text":"PxrLayeredBlend"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:25","text":"PxrMix"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:26","text":"PxrProjectionStack"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:27","text":"PxrRamp"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:28","text":"PxrRemap"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:29","text":"PxrThinFilm"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:30","text":"PxrThreshold"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:31","text":"PxrVary"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:32","text":"几何节点（Geometry Nodes）分类"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:33","text":"你可以使用这些 nodes 来计算几何属性和 vectors。"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:34","text":"PxrDirt"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:35","text":"PxrDispScalarLayer"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:36","text":"PxrDispTransform"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:37","text":"PxrDispVectorLayer"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:38","text":"PxrDot"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:39","text":"PxrCross"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:40","text":"PxrFacingRatio"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:41","text":"PxrTangentField"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:42","text":"脚本节点（Scripting Nodes）分类"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:43","text":"OSL Patterns"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:44","text":"工具节点（Utility Nodes）分类"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:45","text":"PxrAttribute"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:46","text":"PxrMatteID"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:47","text":"PxrPrimvar"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:48","text":"PxrVariable"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:49","text":"PxrToFloat"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:50","text":"PxrToFloat3"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:51","text":"PxrTee"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:52","text":"PxrShadedSide"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:53","text":"纹理烘焙节点（Texture Baking Nodes）分类"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:54","text":"这些 passthrough patterns 旨在让用户能够 bake 任意 pattern networks。"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:55","text":"PxrBakeTexture"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:56","text":"PxrBakePointCloud"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:57","text":"编写自定义 Patterns 的指导（Guidance for Writing Your Own Patterns）"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:58","text":"你不必局限于 RenderMan 提供的 patterns。如果遵循"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:59","text":"OSL Patterns"}
{"item_id":"6491263f8b:60","text":"中的指导，就可以构建自己的 patterns。XPU 只运行 OSL patterns，而 RIS 可同时运行 C++ 和 OSL patterns。"}
